1. Why AS 7?
	1) state-of-the-art & services on-demand 
		The state-of-the-art architecture built on the Modular Service Container enables services on-demand when 
		your application requires them.
	2) certified implementation of the JEE6
		A fast, powerful, implementation of the JEE6 specification. A certified implementation of the JEE6 Web Profile specification.
